        font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.231;">
        <p style="margin-top: 0">您好，为了完成您在 <a href="${url}" style="color: #176093; text-decoration: none" rel="noopener" target="_blank">${title}</a> 的注册流程，请您点击下面的链接以激活您的账号。</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 14pt; font-weight: normal; margin: 10px 0 4px"><a href="${url}api/signup?mail=${mail}&&code=${code}" style="color: #176093; text-decoration: none" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Confirm Account</a></h2>
